Program: Outlook
Title: 03/05/2012
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00r2jt3
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 4 May 2012
Today, Azeri journalist Khadija Ismayilova tells us that her sex life was secretly filmed and posted online after she made allegations about the president's family. The government strongly denies this claim. Also, Akihiro Harako, one of the 'Fukushima Fifty', describes life in the stricken power plant after it was struck by the earthquake and tsunami. Show less